#. type: Content of: <sections><abstract>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Several bootloaders exist. Each one of them has its own way of\n"
"configuration. In this chapter we'll describe all possibilities for you\n"
"and step you through the process of configuring a bootloader to your\n"
"needs.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:21
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Making your Choice"
msgstr "ブートローダの選択"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:23
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:51
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "はじめに"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:27
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Now that your kernel is configured and compiled and the necessary system\n"
"configuration files are filled in correctly, it is time to install a\n"
"program that will fire up your kernel when you start the system. Such a\n"
"program is called a <e>bootloader</e>.\n"
msgstr "さて、カーネルを設定し、コンパイルし、そして必要なシステムの設定ファイルも適切に編集したので、システムを起動するときにカーネルを立ち上げるプログラムをインストールするときが来ました。そのようなプログラムは、<e>ブートローダ</e>と呼ばれています。けれども始める前に、あなたが何を選択するべきか検討しましょう…。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "The bootloader that you use will depend upon the type of PPC machine you have.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:38
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you are using a NewWorld Apple or IBM machine, you need to use \n"
"<uri link=\"#yaboot\">yaboot</uri>.  OldWorld Apple machines have two options,\n"
"<uri link=\"#bootx\">BootX</uri> (recommended) and <uri link=\"#quik\">quik</uri>.\n"
"The Pegasos does not require a bootloader, but you will need to emerge \n"
"<uri link=\"#bootcreator\">bootcreator</uri> to create SmartFirmware boot menus.\n"
msgstr "いくつかのブートローダがLinux/PPC用にあります。<uri link=\"#yaboot\">yaboot</uri>(NewWorldのAppleとIBMマシン用)と<uri link=\"#bootx\">BootX</uri>(OldWorldのAppleマシン用)です。Pegasosはブートローダを必要としませんが、我々はSmartFirmwareブートメニューを作成するために<uri link=\"#bootcreator\">BootCreator</uri>を含めました。\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:49
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Default: Using yaboot"
msgstr "一般的な選択: yabootを使用する"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><impo>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:55
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "yaboot can only be used on NewWorld Apple and IBM systems!\n"
msgstr "yabootはNewWorldのAppleとIBMマシンでのみ使うことができます!\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:59
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"In order to find the boot devices, yaboot needs access to the device nodes\n"
"created by udev on startup and the sysfs filesystem.  These two filesystems\n"
"are found at <path>/dev</path> and <path>sys</path> respectively.  To do this,\n"
"you will need to \"bind mount\" these filesystems from the Installation CD's root\n"
"to the <path>/dev</path> and <path>/sys</path> mount points inside the chroot.\n"
"If you have already bind mounted these filesystems, there is no need to do it\n"
"again.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:68
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Bind-mounting the device and sysfs filesystems"
msgstr "/devファイルシステムをBindマウントする"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:69
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# <i>exit </i> # this will exit the chroot\n"
"# <i>mount --rbind /dev /mnt/gentoo/dev</i>\n"
"# <i>mount --rbind /sys /mnt/gentoo/sys</i>\n"
"# <i>chroot /mnt/gentoo /bin/bash</i>\n"
"# <i>/usr/sbin/env-update &amp;&amp; source /etc/profile </i>\n"
msgstr ""
"# <i>exit </i> # chroot環境から抜けます\n"
"# <i>mount -o bind /dev /mnt/gentoo/dev</i>\n"
"# <i>chroot /mnt/gentoo /bin/bash</i>\n"
"# <i>/usr/sbin/env-update &amp;&amp; source /etc/profile </i>\n"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:77
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To set up yaboot, you can use <c>yabootconfig</c> to automatically create a\n"
"configuration file for you. If you are installing Gentoo on a G5 (where \n"
"<c>yabootconfig</c> does not always work), or you plan to boot from FireWire \n"
"or USB, you will need to manually configure yaboot.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><note>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-ppc-bootloader.xml:84
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
